{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In solving the urban traffic flow prediction challenges, (Wang et al. 2023b) proposed Adaptive SpatioTemporal InceptionNet (AST-InceptionNet), which focuses on the spatio-temporal patterns in congestion-prone areas through the SAGPooling technique, realizing the deep fusion of local and global information.",
    "(Liang et al. 2023d) further proposed a Region-aware Graph Convolutional Network (RGCN), which utilizes Dynamic Time Warping (DTW)-based pooling to capture cross-region spatial correlations and combines with the Transformer model to capture temporal dynamics.",
    "It effectively solved the problem that traditional GNNs make it difficult to capture long-term spatial and temporal dependencies.",
    "It adopted the spectral clustering algorithm as the pooling method, which provided a scientific basis for the regional division of the transportation network and further improved the prediction accuracy.",
    "In the field of SQPF, (Wu et al. 2022b) proposed Inductive spatiotemporal Graph Convolutional Networks (InstGCNs) to effectively aggregate spatial information among nodes through a maximum pooling technique, which achieves accurate modeling of complex precipitation systems."
  ],
